        <p>October: 50 Public Lab members from around the world spent 4 days <a href="/notes/Shannon/10-23-2013/public-lab-focuses-on-open-science-education-at-2013-barnraising">working together at the 2013 Barnraising in New Orleans</a> focusing on education, from curriculum development to field methods.</p>
