        <h2>Kite Photos reveal coal dumping in the Mississippi River</h2>
        <p>May: GRN and Clean Gulf Commerce Coalition filed a notice of intent to sue United Bulk for Clean Water Act violations, based on <a href="/notes/eustatic/05-28-2013/kite-photos-of-ongoing-coal-pollution-in-plaquemines-parish-la">this crucial photo by Scott Eustis</a>.</p>
